              <p class="faq__a">This line covers crypto you received without selling something — such as <strong>staking rewards</strong>, <strong>DeFi interest</strong>, <strong>airdrops</strong>, and <strong>referral bonuses</strong>. The app tracks these separately from your buy/sell gains so you have a complete picture of where your crypto came from.</p>
